{
  "chapter": 154,
  "chapter_summary": "第154章\"野火晚宴\"讲述泾水东岸田猎后的露天宴会。吕不韦在猎前向项少龙宣布将由太后朱姬亲自主持他与吕娘蓉的婚事，项少龙表面应承心中暗喜。宴前嬴盈因项少龙表演飞针而心生爱慕，主动找他\"算帐\"实为修好，两人言归于好并约定初更后相会。晚宴上吕不韦向小盘敬酒歌功颂德，管中邪挑衅项少龙再展飞针绝技。吕娘蓉在众人面前哭泣拒婚\"我不嫁他了\"，吕不韦被迫暂时取消婚事。朱姬私下召见项少龙，流露幽怨之情，暗示每次都将嫪毐当作项少龙。宴会后嬴盈与鹿丹儿找管中邪斗酒，荆俊凭矫捷身手赢得鹿丹儿青睐。小盘宣布人事调动，封吕不韦为\"仲父\"，擢升嫪毐为内史。纪嫣然提醒项少龙管中邪在觊觎嬴盈，并追问他对琴清的感情。荆俊与鹿丹儿互生情愫，项少龙鼓励他趁机追求。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "吕不韦",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我和太后说了，待会儿野宴时由她亲自宣布少龙和娘蓉的婚事。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "吕不韦",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙该没有异议吧！",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "text": "我只怕自己配不上三小姐。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "吕不韦",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我最欢喜少龙的谦虚，待我搬到新相府，立即择日为你两人成亲，好了却这桩心事。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "吕不韦",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "高陵君方面有什么动静？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "text": "我已着人暗中监视他，不过却发现不到他另有伏兵，或者是我们多疑了。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "吕不韦",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "小心点总是好的，这事全权交给你处理。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "吕不韦",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙！你是否仍在怀疑我的诚意呢？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "text": "吕相何出此言？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "吕不韦",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙不用瞒我，那晚中邪请你到醉风楼喝酒，见到你把单美美敬的酒暗泼到几下去。唉！你以为那是毒酒吗？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "text": "正如吕相所言，小心点总是好的吧！",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "吕不韦",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "娘蓉成了你项家的人后，少龙就是我的好女婿，那时该可放心喝酒了吧。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_ying",
      "speaker_name": "嬴盈",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项少龙！我嬴盈是否很讨你的厌，找你较量时，总是推三推四，又赖腿伤不便，怎么在储君前却能表演飞针绝技，现在谁都知道你不给面子人家，这笔帐该怎么和你算？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ying_ying",
      "text": "好吧！算我不对，不过腿伤确非凭空捏造，我大可脱下裤子给你检查！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_ying",
      "speaker_name": "嬴盈",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "谁要检查你？我要你再掷给我们看。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ying_ying",
      "text": "今天我掷针时，伤口又迸裂开来，让我们找别的事儿玩吧！",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_ying",
      "speaker_name": "嬴盈",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "玩什么好呢？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ying_ying",
      "text": "你的营帐在哪里？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_ying",
      "speaker_name": "嬴盈",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你在看什么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ying_ying",
      "text": "哪个男人不爱看女人的身体，嬴大小姐何用大惊小怪？这样吧！初更后我到你的营地来找你，到时给足你面子，好让你下了这口气。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_ying",
      "speaker_name": "嬴盈",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "一言为定。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ying_ying",
      "text": "到时不要又布下陷阱来害我，哼！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_ying",
      "speaker_name": "嬴盈",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "谁有闲情去害你哩！记着了！假若你失约的话，嬴盈一生一世都会恨你的。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_ying",
      "speaker_name": "嬴盈",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我的营帐在王营之西，旗是紫色的，帐门处绣了一朵紫花，切莫忘记。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "吕不韦",
      "listener": "char_xiao_pan",
      "text": "听说储君你射下一头大雁，此乃天大吉兆，我大秦今年必然风调雨顺，国泰民安。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "text": "右相国，寡人和你喝一杯。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guan_zhong_xie",
      "speaker_name": "管中邪",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项大人待会儿在储君主持的晚艺会上，肯否再表演一次五针同发的惊世秘技？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_guan_zhong_xie",
      "text": "献丑不如藏拙，我还未看过管大人铁弓的威力，管大人可否偿我所愿？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guan_zhong_xie",
      "speaker_name": "管中邪",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "只要项大人吩咐，下属怎敢不从命，若非大人腿伤，真想和大人切磋两招，享受一下受高手指教的乐趣。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "吕不韦",
      "listener": "char_lv_niang_rong",
      "text": "娘蓉你给爹好好伺候项大人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_niang_rong",
      "speaker_name": "吕娘蓉",
      "listener": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "text": "项大人可没有和娘蓉说话啊！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "吕不韦",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙！快给我哄得娘蓉开开心心的。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "text": "晓得了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_lv_niang_rong",
      "text": "三小姐今天猎到什么回来呢？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_niang_rong",
      "speaker_name": "吕娘蓉",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "今天我没有打猎的兴致。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_lv_niang_rong",
      "text": "不是我项少龙破坏三小姐的兴致吧？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "吕不韦",
      "listener": "char_lv_niang_rong",
      "text": "娘蓉！要不要回帐歇歇？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_niang_rong",
      "speaker_name": "吕娘蓉",
      "listener": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "text": "我不嫁他了！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guan_zhong_xie",
      "speaker_name": "管中邪",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项大人说得对！",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "吕不韦",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "暂时取消婚事，迟些再说。唉！少龙！我不知该怎么说。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "text": "吕相不用介怀。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙不用多礼，请坐！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ji",
      "text": "太后有何赐示？",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙！你和政儿都变了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ji",
      "text": "太后！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我不想听言不由衷的话，唉！你们是否心中在怪我呢？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "每次我都是把他当作是你，明白吗？",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项统领可以退下了！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guan_zhong_xie",
      "speaker_name": "管中邪",
      "listener": "char_lu_dan_er",
      "text": "我奉项大人之命，待会儿要活动一下。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guan_zhong_xie",
      "speaker_name": "管中邪",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项大人若想看末将献丑，请代我接过两位小姐的挑战。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_guan_zhong_xie",
      "text": "管大人真会说话！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_dan_er",
      "speaker_name": "鹿丹儿",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "算你识相，我们讲和好吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_jun",
      "speaker_name": "荆俊",
      "listener": "char_lu_dan_er",
      "text": "两位大小姐想灌醉我三哥吗？得先过我这关才成。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_dan_er",
      "speaker_name": "鹿丹儿",
      "listener": "char_jing_jun",
      "text": "难道我们会怕你小俊儿？",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wen_jun",
      "speaker_name": "昌文君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项大人收到小妹和丹儿的红花吗？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_dan_er",
      "speaker_name": "鹿丹儿",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "给他有用吗？一个跛子做得出什么事来？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_chang_wen_jun",
      "text": "什么红花？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_jun",
      "speaker_name": "荆俊",
      "listener": "char_lu_dan_er",
      "text": "花可以给三哥，行动则由小弟代为执行。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wen_jun",
      "speaker_name": "昌文君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "是我们大秦的风俗，田猎之时，未嫁少女若看上心仪男子，便赠他一朵手绣的红花，持花者三更后可到她帐内度宿，嘿！明白了吧！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_ying",
      "speaker_name": "嬴盈",
      "listener": "char_chang_wen_jun",
      "text": "二兄你只懂乱说话。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_dan_er",
      "speaker_name": "鹿丹儿",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我还未决定把花送谁，待晚艺会时再看看吧。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_jing_jun",
      "text": "小俊！丹儿小姐在提点你了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wen_jun",
      "speaker_name": "昌文君",
      "listener": "char_jing_jun",
      "text": "那是否由你五弟取花，实际行动却由你执行？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_jun",
      "speaker_name": "荆俊",
      "listener": "char_lu_dan_er",
      "text": "若我得到两位美人儿的红花，就把嬴小姐的送给三哥，丹儿姑娘的留下自享，噢！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_dan_er",
      "speaker_name": "鹿丹儿",
      "listener": "char_jing_jun",
      "text": "小俊猴儿！再翻两转来看看。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_jun",
      "speaker_name": "荆俊",
      "listener": "char_lu_dan_er",
      "text": "若你变作雌猴，我就扮雄猴带你到树上翻跟斗。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wen_jun",
      "speaker_name": "昌文君",
      "listener": "char_jing_jun",
      "text": "只是这一手，丹儿就要把红花送你。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_ying",
      "speaker_name": "嬴盈",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "莫忘记你答应过的事。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ying_ying",
      "text": "承诺作废，又说讲和修好，刚才竟公然在我眼前找别的男人，人家拒绝了才拿我做代替品。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_ying",
      "speaker_name": "嬴盈",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "不是那样的，人家其实是想来……啊！你算什么？我为何要向你解释？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ying_ying",
      "text": "好吧！当我怕了你大小姐，做代替品就代替品吧！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_ying",
      "speaker_name": "嬴盈",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "都说你不是代替品了，人家一直……不说了！你试试看不来找我吧！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ying_ying",
      "text": "那朵红花呢？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "夫君回复以前的风流本色了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "夫君小心一点，刚才管中邪一直在注视你们，他或会加以破坏，嬴盈始终是王族的人，管中邪得她为妻该是有利无害。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "自倩公主和春盈等离世后，我已心如死灰，只希望和你们好好度过下半生。假若嬴盈要投入管中邪的怀抱，由得她吧！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你敢说对清姊没有动心吗？",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "你为何要提起她呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "刚才你们两人在帐内说了些什么话？为何她离开时耳根都红透了，还神情暧昧？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "我像平时般说话吧！只是她的脸皮太嫩了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "清姊是个非常有自制力的人，只是对你动了真情，才变得脸皮薄了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "是我不好！唉！为何我总会惹上这种烦恼？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "谁叫你人长得英俊，心地又善良，口才更了得，否则我也不会给你的什么'绝对的权力，使人绝对腐化'那类花言巧语骗上手。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 456,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "这种至理名言竟当是花言巧语，看我肯饶你不？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "谁要你饶哩！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 462,
      "line_end": 462
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_jun",
      "speaker_name": "荆俊",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "晚艺会开始，三哥、三嫂还在卿卿我我吗？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 466
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_jun",
      "speaker_name": "荆俊",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这妮子够骚劲，给我摸了几把还要追来，后来我抱头让她揍一顿，她表面凶巴巴的，但下手不知多么顾着我，真是精彩。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 472,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_jing_jun",
      "text": "要夺得美人归，须趁这两天，你可明白？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 154,
      "line_start": 476,
      "line_end": 478
    }
